text: Ivan Graanoogst is a Surinamese soldier and politician. He was the acting military ruler of Suriname from 24 December 1990 to 29 December 1990, after a military coup that removed the democratic government of President Ramsewak Shankar from power. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Presidents of Suriname
title: Ivan Graanoogst
